<div id="community-vibe">
    <h2 class="sect-title">Community Vibe in Penbrooke Meadows</h2>
    <div class="col-grid-2">
        <div>
            <p class="par-xl">Established back in 1969, the community in Penbrooke Meadows is particularly desired for the quaint charm of its mid-century architecture and landscaping. </p>
            <p class="par-lg">A medium-sized residential community in South East Calgary, Penbrooke Meadows is a highly desirable neighborhood in the city. </p>
            <p class="par-lg">Given its compact size, the community offers its residents quick access to a host of schools, shopping malls and recreational venues.</p>
        </div>
